a Trap, which is basically warning that the union sphere in the US is very heavily legislated,

38:13.560 --> 38:17.960
and there's lots of sort of bad political context when it comes to saying, we should

38:17.960 --> 38:21.840
have a union for this, basically being something that you shouldn't ask for unless you really

38:21.840 --> 38:24.840
know what you're getting into.

