40:29.600 --> 40:31.640
maybe looking at some of the smaller ones.

40:31.640 --> 40:35.400
Or if you work at Amazon, check out Amazon Workers United.

40:35.400 --> 40:38.640
If you're at Google, check out Alphabet Workers United.

40:38.640 --> 40:43.920
There are existing unions within these companies, even if they aren't contract unions.

